{"tid":485833,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"你第一日跌,我覺得冇乜野","createTime":"2017-12-01T09:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T16:33:05.000Z","uid":70429,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0a7d3f0a535246a18a4acb76f361379cb11cd4","tid":485833,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"畢竟回調下係好事,<br />\n<br />\n學班文青話齋:''<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b7l5dtj0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb7l5dtj0&h=cde82b8b&s={SIZE}\" />''<br />\n<br />\n我恨不得你回調到420蚊比次機會我入多d.<br />\n<br />\n結果你一日日地妹下妹下妹落去410,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xr7gk5p6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxr7gk5p6&h=235129ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對我來講,喜出望外之於更有些許心慌.<br />\n<br />\n但我沒有騰雞,繼續訊你,<br />\n<br />\n你是誰?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gtimg.com/11/1180/118057/11805777_980x1200_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gtimg.com%2F11%2F1180%2F118057%2F11805777_980x1200_0.jpg&h=ad131e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n''亞洲股王''<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你應該休息夠了,夠鐘啟程了,<br />\n<br />\n果然,<br />\n<br />\n你谷底反彈20蚊果日,眾人嘩然,<br />\n<br />\n但我並不感到意外.<br />\n<br />\n因為你只是拎翻你應得既價值.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vpyub9lc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvpyub9lc&h=e6853cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日,或者後日,最多一個禮拜,<br />\n<br />\n你就會重上439,直奔450.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日係12月1日.<br />\n<br />\n你的收市價係385蚊.<br />\n<br />\n同半個月前一樣.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hzmwu710\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhzmwu710&h=3f663fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離我們的夢想距離65蚊.<br />\n<br />\n離我的家鄉距離40蚊."},{"pid":"013b3cb0fedcabaf486cb4d695e64397acc444e3","tid":485833,"uid":3682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"唔好咁迷訊"},{"pid":"3c5cc5023bd61735fc9f2d1868d2476d5fa85c31","tid":485833,"uid":70429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁迷訊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n騎虎難下"},{"pid":"b9ae40d122846a6e9b89766ccd3bcc92baeed73a","tid":485833,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"買左幾多呀？<br />\n<br />\n得一兩手就咪撚叫春"},{"pid":"66bc4aaf75803458e2dd7f526c51429fdbf60916","tid":485833,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"3988, 4蚊入, 跌到落3.8, 我都未叫春啦"},{"pid":"02d04734140ba2d72707b2598a04ba2133a4c561","tid":485833,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3988, 4蚊入, 跌到落3.8, 我都未叫春啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daee7b4e8e557c6800d88658e95c40bf95d9bd8b","tid":485833,"uid":51965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"380牛我叫唔叫得春 渣左37000蚊"},{"pid":"48ab175692b5da9dd68b847703139ac8f284e72a","tid":485833,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3988, 4蚊入, 跌到落3.8, 我都未叫春啦</blockquote><br />\n$200<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69549f93aa7d64fb0ffd481e782c6c963185815d","tid":485833,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"只要訊"},{"pid":"36a82a73ea298f5f54df61c578e88e5ef79a5565","tid":485833,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-0